      <acqinfo id="aspace_a0bef6e2060c8300e784e2204192226e">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The Drama 50 Script Collection was housed in the former Drama Library until its transfer to the Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library in 2008.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_97fe5b210fc91c33034d2a0feee3ba6a">
