         <p>Copyright has not been transferred to Yale University.</p>  
      </userestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_fdf90b5fcf4bb962f4c1c24e6fe90a5c">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Drama 50 Script Collection, Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library, Yale University.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_5b08edb007c8d9e2369783b4a82b43b5">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection contains scripts and other materials produced as part of the Drama 50 course at the Yale School of Drama. During the semester-long Drama 50 course, students from various disciplines within the School of Drama create and perform 20-minute long collaborative works of theater.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_2df6551471f1e77d8d160a51b1093713">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arranged chronologically, then alphabetically by title within each year.</p>  
      </arrangement>
